---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Lifecycle Governance — DID One" description="Lifecycle governance for every identity and every agent.">
  <main class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="badge">Lifecycle Governance</div>
      <h1>Lifecycle for every agent</h1>
      <p class="lede">No agent exists outside lifecycle. No agent acts outside governance. No agent keeps autonomy after trust breaks.</p>
      <div class="panel">
        <pre class="code-card">0  unborn
1  requested
2  registered
3  verified
4  provisioned
5  active
6  monitored
7  constrained
8  probation
9  suspended
10 revoked
11 graceful_exit_requested
12 handoff_in_progress
13 exited
14 retired
15 archived
16 backward_compatible</pre>
      </div>
      <div class="grid" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <div class="card"><h3>Capability</h3><p>Capability can grow through learning, evidence, and credentials.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Autonomy</h3><p>Autonomy is granted by governance, never assumed from capability.</p></div>
        <div class="card"><h3>Audit</h3><p>Every lifecycle transition writes immutable evidence and remains replayable.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
